        "name": "Wildfire",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "A thin layer of ash and flame covers the ground in the area. The area becomes hazardous terrain. A creature that moves on the ground through the area takes 1 fire damage for every square of that area it moves into. A creature that ends its turn in the area must succeed at a Reflex save or take 1 persistent fire damage.  \n  \n Each time you Sustain this spell, the radius of the burst increases by 5 feet.",
